query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 0 and PerC.BirthDate < getdate() and PerC.DeathDate is null

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 0 and PerC.BirthDate > getdate() and PerC.DeathDate is null

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '??.??.' + cast(year(PerC.BirthDate) as varchar(4)) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 1 and month(PerC.BirthDate) != 1 and PerC.DeathDate is null

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '??.??.' + cast(year(PerC.BirthDate) as varchar(4)) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 1 and month(PerC.BirthDate) = 1 and PerC.DeathDate is null
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 0 and PerC.DeathDate is null

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, convert(varchar, PerC.BirthDate, 104) + ' - ' + convert(varchar, PerC.DeathDate, 104) OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.BirthDateIsUndefined = 0 and PerC.DeathDate is not null
